item.title: CVE-2024-5166|2024-05-22T16:11:55.740Z -- Google Cloud -- Looker
item.description: An Insecure Direct Object Reference in Google Cloud's Looker allowed metadata exposure across authenticated Looker users sharing the same LookML model.
